    Can be used to start Vadere in [lock] mode.

    Receives an object of type ScenarioStore, manages a scenario and runs the simulation.

    Contains the data for a Vadere object that can be serialized.

    A VadereProject holds a list of ScenarioRunManagers and functionality to manage them.
